81
00:08:43,730 --> 00:08:48,790
The schedule didn't change. It's just a meeting.

82
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:51,760
Take him to your place, not mine.

83
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,760
My place is a total mess right now.

84
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,380
Okay.

85
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:02,350
Come here. Come.

86
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:23,150
Go wait somewhere.

87
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:26,800
I'll tell you what we talked about.

88
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,900
Let me explain.

89
00:09:30,770 --> 00:09:32,740
Explain?

90
00:09:32,740 --> 00:09:34,500
Justify?

91
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:40,320
I don't think stuff like that could fix this.

92
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:44,460
You're all educated, and you teach children.

93
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:46,620
If I explain rationally—

94
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:48,650
Goodness ...

95
00:09:48,650 --> 00:09:52,510
Lee Jun Ho,  Your Highness Teacher!

96
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:58,970
The problem is that they're educated, and they teach students.

97
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:03,130
What do you mean?

98
00:10:03,130 --> 00:10:08,250
Things will get worse since they're all rational.

99
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:10,770
And tons of people inside and outside the academy have been waiting

100
00:10:10,770 --> 00:10:13,730
