104
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:40,130
An academy lecturer who had the most students from some high school got cancer.

105
00:10:40,130 --> 00:10:43,690
It was still in an early stage, and it was curable.

106
00:10:43,690 --> 00:10:45,580
But in less than a day,

107
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:50,770
the rumor that he was terminally ill and would be dying soon spread.

108
