109
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:00,330
That's how this industry is.

110
00:11:04,110 --> 00:11:08,130
I don't think Team Leader Seo and you

111
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:13,850
did anything that's so bad.

112
00:11:16,260 --> 00:11:18,400
So...

113
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:24,700
go out and wait while drinking coffee, huh?

114
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:29,210
I'm asking who told you to come.

115
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:31,020
Listen to me. I'll keep it short.

116
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:32,660
I asked who told you?

117
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:34,270
I did.

118
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,640
What?

119
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,480
We'll talk amongst ourselves for a bit.

120
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:43,990
But isn't it okay to listen to Team Leader Seo?

121
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:48,740
It'd be hard to be objective, then.

122
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:51,470
I don't even know why she needs to explain.

123
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:56,690
No, hold on. It's not just that they fell for each other.

124
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:59,920
She's supposed to be a team leader

125
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:02,450
