131
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:18,820
Huiwon High is our academy's—

132
00:12:18,820 --> 00:12:24,150
Shouldn't you tell us if you're really dating first?

133
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:29,640
Mr. Lee is...

134
