148
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:05,950
Didn't you let Jun Ho teach that class?

149
00:14:05,950 --> 00:14:07,950
Be quiet if you don't know.

150
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:09,540
What do I not know?

151
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,420
How parents feel.

152
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:13,200
What are you talking about?

153
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:17,150
To send their child to a good school,

154
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:21,270
the mothers, fathers, grandmothers, and grandfathers are all

155
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:23,250
making a fuss about it.

156
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:25,580
But the teachers were doing that at the academy?

157
00:14:25,580 --> 00:14:27,460
How could they let someone like that teach their child?

158
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:29,300
What do you think they did?

159
00:14:29,300 --> 00:14:32,480
What kind of rumors spread overnight, anyway?

160
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,890
I'm just predicting how this will go.

161
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:40,440
It started.

162
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:45,270
Yes, Ah Jeong's mother.

163
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:48,800
Yes, yes. What made you call so early?

164
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:51,850
Pardon? No.

165
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:13,750
 Hey, looks like there's a weird rumor about you. 

166
00:15:23,620 --> 00:15:25,380
 Are you okay? 

167
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:37,400
What did you say to me? After what you guys did?

168
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:39,680
I said I pity your students!

169
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:42,550
"You?" Come here, you bastard!

170
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:45,410
We don't live together, and we didn't do anything shameful.

171
00:15:45,410 --> 00:15:47,230
Why are you calling me names?

172
00:15:47,230 --> 00:15:49,390
