174
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:54,290
Let go! I'm calm.

175
00:15:54,290 --> 00:15:56,240
Gosh, what a joke.

176
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,980
Team Leader.

177
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:01,640
This isn't right.

178
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:04,050
- What?
 - Please.

179
00:16:04,050 --> 00:16:06,120
