181
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:11,400
- Jun Ho's behavior explains everything. 
- Team Leader.

182
00:16:13,330 --> 00:16:15,230
Team Leader,

183
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:18,430
I don't think you have time for this.

184
00:16:22,130 --> 00:16:23,800
Okay.

185
00:16:28,730 --> 00:16:29,950
Why are you giving this to me?

186
00:16:29,950 --> 00:16:33,700
You have pretty handwriting. I haven't handwritten things in a long time.

187
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:35,420
What should I write?

188
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:38,670
Thank him for letting you do well in the finals.

189
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,850
And ask for good results next year, too.

190
00:16:40,850 --> 00:16:43,520
Shouldn't you say that to my teachers instead?

191
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:48,620
I pay them every month. It's a lot of money.

192
00:16:48,620 --> 00:16:51,760
Write quickly and go to the academy. Pray quickly, too.

193
00:16:58,020 --> 00:17:00,130
- Seong Ha Yul.
 - Yes.

194
00:17:00,130 --> 00:17:03,350
Give me Seo Hye Jin's textbook. The handouts and the homework, too.

195
00:17:03,350 --> 00:17:05,080
All of a sudden? Here?

196
00:17:05,080 --> 00:17:06,730
Hurry.

197
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:24,900
How about the rest?

198
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:26,490
I don't have the handouts.

199
00:17:26,490 --> 00:17:29,530
The homework is previewing what we'll learn next.

200
00:17:29,530 --> 00:17:31,450
- Is that all?
 - Yes.

201
00:17:31,450 --> 00:17:34,210
She wanted us to change the way we study.

202
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:37,980
She's crazy.

203
00:17:54,890 --> 00:17:57,190
Yes, this is Sin Dae Baek, Director.

204
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:03,060
Yes, what made you call?

205
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:09,240
Yes, I'm at Daechi Chase.

206
00:18:11,530 --> 00:18:12,900
Yes.

207
