216
00:19:00,330 --> 00:19:05,440
Jeong Su takes notes thoroughly for a boy, and he pays attention in class.

217
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:06,470
Yes.

218
00:19:06,470 --> 00:19:08,910
But there's no sign of him studying.

219
00:19:08,910 --> 00:19:11,200
Same with Ye Eun.

220
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:13,000
Something's not right.

221
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:18,450
She used to give them tons of homework, mock tests, and handouts before.

222
00:19:18,450 --> 00:19:20,320
She said she won't check the homework, either.

223
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:23,480
Doesn't this mean she stopped caring for them?

224
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:28,310
She doesn't check the homework. The TA does. Why?

225
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:36,190
Can she not handle it physically?

226
00:19:36,190 --> 00:19:38,130
Because she's dating a younger man?

227
00:19:38,770 --> 00:19:40,800
Are you crazy?

228
00:19:40,800 --> 00:19:44,800
You're talking about Seo Hye Jin, right?

229
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:46,270
Yes.

230
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:49,710
Can we join you?

231
00:19:49,710 --> 00:19:52,240
Yes, go ahead.

232
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,420
Are your kids starting 11th grade?

233
00:20:05,420 --> 00:20:07,150
Yes.

234
00:20:07,150 --> 00:20:08,800
Same with us.

235
00:20:10,810 --> 00:20:14,260
I don't think this should be taken lightly.

236
00:20:15,690 --> 00:20:19,130
You know the teacher who was her student? Lee Jun Ho?

237
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:20,750
Yes.

238
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:23,180
I heard he used to work for Cheongwun Group.

239
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:25,640
What about that?

240
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:29,850
She made her student quit his good job and join the academy.

241
00:20:29,850 --> 00:20:32,810
That's a serious thing to do.

242
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:40,490
He was her only student when she first started working in Daechi-dong.

243
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:45,380
She must've provided him with...

244
00:20:47,370 --> 00:20:50,430
an intense experience he couldn't forget.

245
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:53,300
 Gosh... 

246
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:56,180
- You're taking it too far. 
- I know.

247
00:20:56,820 --> 00:20:59,270
You must have a daughter.

248
00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:00,510
Yes.

249
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,520
I know because I have a son.

250
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:05,460
You have no idea

251
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:08,500
how hot-blooded teenage boys are.

252
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:12,900
- My gosh. No way. 
- If that's true...

253
00:21:12,900 --> 00:21:14,640
That's so gross.

254
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,420
What's gross? Huh?

255
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:19,780
It all hit the fan. Have a seat.

256
00:21:19,780 --> 00:21:21,620
Seriously.

257
00:21:22,910 --> 00:21:26,020
 I know. They totally lost their minds. 

258
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:29,730
They hang out in the classrooms every night.

259
00:21:29,730 --> 00:21:32,210
In the classrooms?

260
00:21:32,210 --> 00:21:33,880
Hello, Director.

261
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,930
Director,

262
00:21:35,930 --> 00:21:37,630
this is amazing.

263
00:21:38,330 --> 00:21:43,680
Daechi Chase somehow has major problems as soon as Mr. Pyo joined us.

264
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:46,770
Looks like you're having a very lucky year.

265
00:21:46,770 --> 00:21:48,460
I'm not sure what you're referring to.

266
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:51,970
You know Seo Hye Jin? The one from the "Teacher-Pupil Tag Team."

267
00:21:51,970 --> 00:21:54,920
